    les_parametres[2] = "diag";

    les_parametres[4] = "nb_it_max";

  }

  Motcle motlu;
  is >> motlu;

    {
      Cerr << "Error when reading the GMRES parameters " << finl;
      Cerr << "One expected " << accolade_ouverte
           << " instead of : " << motlu << finl;
      exit();
    }
  is >> motlu;
  while (motlu != accolade_fermee)
    {
      rang = les_parametres.search(motlu);
      switch(rang)
        {
        case 0:
          {
            fixer_limpr(1);
            break;
          }
        case 8:
          {
            fixer_limpr(-1);
            break;
          }
        case 1:

            is >> seuil_;
            break;
          }
        case 2:
          {
            is_local_gmres=1;
            precond_diag=1;
            break;
          }
        case 3:
          {
            is_local_gmres=1;
            precond_diag=0;
            break;
          }
        case 4:
          {
            is>>nb_it_max_;
            break;
          }

          {

            break;

            break;
          }
        case 7:

            is >>dim_espace_Krilov_;
            break;
          }

          {
            Cerr << "Error when reading the Gmres parameters " << finl;
            Cerr << "One expected a word among " << les_parametres
                 << " instead of " << motlu << finl;
            exit();
          }
        }
      is >> motlu;
    }
  return is;
